0far%20beyond%20Japan%2C%20inspiring%20generations%20of%20artists%20and%20animators%20worldwide.%20Its%20films%20are%20known%20for%20their%20rich%20storytelling%2C%20breathtaking%20visuals%2C%20and%20deep%20themes%20exploring%20nature%2C%20identity%2C%20and%20human%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20commercial%20success%2C%20Ghibli%20is%20revered%20for%20its%20meticulous%20hand-drawn%20animation%2C%20use%20of%20watercolor%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20philosophical%20depth%20that%20resonates%20with%20audiences%20of%20all%20ages.%20The%20studio%20is%20known%20for%20its%20strong%20female%20protagonists%2C%20immersive%20worlds%2C%20and%20narratives%20that%20blend%20Japanese%20folklore%20with%20universal%20human%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Studio%20Ghibli%20opened%20the%20Ghibli%20Museum%20in%20Mitaka%2C%20Tokyo%2C%20offering%20fans%20an%20interactive%20experience%20with%20behind-the-scenes%20insights%20into%20their%20creative%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20Miyazaki%E2%80%99s%20brief%20retirement%20in%202013%20(before%20his%20return%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Boy%20and%20the%20Heron%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202023)%2C%20Ghibli%20remains%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20global%20animation%2C%20influencing%20artists%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F97551%2F10-foreign-films-must-watch-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilmmakers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20pop%20culture%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAI%20meets%20Ghibli%3A%20what%20do%20Indian%20artists%20think%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98fun%20thing%E2%80%99%20for%20many%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20there%20is%20another%20group%20of%20netizens%20who%20question%20this%20move%20by%20ChatGPT.%20Why%3F%20For%20two%20reasons%2C%20one%20Ghibli%20anime%20makes%20scary%20images%20look%20dreamy%20and%20nice%20to%20the%20eyes%2C%20and%20secondly%2C%20a%20few%20artists%20feel%20that%20it%20devalues%20the%20work%20of%20real%20artists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20spoke%20to%20Krishna%20(name%20changed)%2C%20Game%20Designer%20at%20a%20leading%20organisation%20in%20India%2C%20who%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20been%20associated%20with%20games%20and%20digital%20art%20for%20over%202%20decades%20now%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20to%20explore%20a%20variety%20of%20art%20styles%20as%20an%20artist%20and%20one%20draws%20inspiration%20from%20a%20number%20of%20sources.%20In%20an%20age%20of%20AI%2C%20it%20has%20become%20imperative%20to%20us%2C%20as%20artists%2C%20to%20explore%20various%20AI%20tools%20to%20quickly%20churn%20out%20multiple%20ideas%20with%20just%20a%20click%20of%20a%20button.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20shared%20his%20perspective%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20feel%20that%20art%20cannot%20be%20replaced%20altogether%20by%20AI%2C%20it%20has%20definitely%20made%20inroads%20into%20the%20art%20production%20pipeline%2C%20saving%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20manual%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F126067%2Fartist-teju-behan-art%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F126067%2Fartist-teju-behan-art%2F%5C%22%3E%20art%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Is%20it%20my%20personal%20opinion%20that%20AI-generated%20image