%20300%20atomic%20bombs%20combined%2C%20according%20to%20a%20leading%20American%20geologist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20force%20that%20a%20quake%20like%20this%20releases%20is%20about%20334%20atomic%20bombs%2C%26quot%3B%20geologist%20Jess%20Phoenix%20told%20CNN.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Phoenix%20also%20warned%20that%20aftershocks%20from%20the%20quake%2C%20which%20struck%20Myanmar%20on%20Friday%2C%20%26quot%3Bcould%20persist%20for%20months.%26quot%3B%20She%20noted%20that%20this%20would%20happen%20because%20the%20Indian%20tectonic%20plate%20continues%20to%20crash%20with%20the%20Eurasian%20plate%20beneath%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20geologist%20further%20noted%20that%20there%20could%20be%20hindrances%20in%20grasping%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20the%20catastrophe%20as%20the%20devastation%20in%20Myanmar%20will%20only%20be%20worsened%20by%20the%20country's%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20would%20normally%20be%20a%20difficult%20situation%20becomes%20almost%20impossible%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERescue%20Operations%20Continue%20In%20Myanmar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20operations%20continued%20in%20Mandalay%20and%20other%20areas%20in%20Myanmar%20after%20the%20deadly%20earthquake%2C%20but%20hopes%20of%20finding%20more%20survivors%20in%20the%20rubble%20are%20fading%20amid%20difficult%20conditions%20--%20with%20temperatures%20expected%20to%20reach%20around%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20(104%20Fahrenheit).%20Some%20residents%20spent%20a%20third%20night%20sleeping%20in%20the%20open%2C%20with%20aftershocks%20continuing%20to%20rock%20the%20central%20Myanmar%20city%20of%20more%20than%201.7%20million%20people%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sticky%20heat%20has%20exhausted%20rescue%20workers%20and%20accelerated%20body%20decomposition%2C%20which%20could%20complicate%20identification%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20desperate%20scene%20unfolded%20at%20a%20collapsed%20apartment%20block%20in%20Myanmar's%20second%20biggest%20city%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20when%20rescuers%20thought%20they%20had%20saved%20the%20life%20of%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20trapped%20under%20the%20rubble%20for%20more%20than%2055%20hours.%20They%20amputated%20her%20leg%20to%20free%20her%2C%20but%20after%20pulling%20her%20out%2C%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20everything%20to%20save%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20medical%20responders%20told%20AFP%2C%20but%20she%20had%20lost%20too%20much%20blood%20from%20the%20amputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20worshipers%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20gathered%20near%20a%20destroyed%20mosque%20in%20the%20city%20on%20Monday%20morning%20for%20the%20first%20prayer%20of%20Eid%20al-Fitr%2C%20the%20holiday%20that%20follows%20the%20Islamic%20fasting%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunerals%20for%20hundreds%20of%20victims%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%207.7-magnitude%20quake%20struck%20near%20Mandalay%20early%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20followed%20minutes%20later%20by%20a%206.7-magnitude%20aftershock.%20The%20tremors%20collapsed%20buildings%2C%20downed%20bridges%20and%20buckled%20roads%2C%20with%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20destruction%20seen%20in%20central%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Federation%20of%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Societies%20launched%20an%20emergency%20appeal%20Sunday%20for%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%20to%20help%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20largest%20humanitarian%20network%20said%20needs%20were%20growing%20by%20the%20hour%20as%20rising%20temperatures%20and%20the%20approaching%20monsoon%20season%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20%26quot%3Bsecondary%20crises%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20facing%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20country%20of%20over%2050%20million%20people%20were%20immense%20even%20before%20the%20earthquake.%20Myanmar%20has%20been%20ravaged%20by%20four%20years%20of%20civil%20war%20sparked%20by%20a%20military%20coup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20have%20emerged%20of%20sporadic%20fighting%20even%20after%20the%20quake%2C%20with%20one%20rebel%20group%20telling%20AFP%20on%20Sunday%20that%20seven%20of%20its%20fighters%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20aerial%20attack%20soon%20after%20the%20tremors%20hit.%20Before%20Friday's%20quake%2C%20some%203.5%20million%20people%20were%20displaced%20by%20the%20raging%20civil%20war%2C%20many%20at%20risk%20of%20hunger.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743394980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fhkmls91_myanmar-earthquake_625x300_31_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeadly-myanmar-earthquake-unleashed-energy-of-334-atomic-bombs-report-8051164%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20powerful%207.7-magnitude%20earthquake%2C%20which%20killed%20around%201700%20people%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20has%20unleashed%20energy%20equivalent%20to%20over%20300%20atomic%20bombs%20combined%2C%20according%20to%20a%20leading%20American%20geologist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeadly-myanmar-earthquake-unleashed-energy-of-334-atomic-bombs-report-8051164%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ash%2C%20Aaradhya%2C%20Abhishek%20pose%20for%20a%20family%20pic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743394958000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119787338%2Cimgsize-44864.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faishwarya-rai-aaradhya-and-abhishek-bachchan-pose-for-a-happy-family-picture-at-cousins-wedding%2Farticleshow%2F119787431.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22http