ngs%20(CSK)%20in%20the%206-run%20defeat%20against%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20(RR)%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20has%20seen%20Dhoni%20bat%20quite%20down%20in%20the%20order%2C%20ranging%20from%20No.%207%20to%20No.%209.%20Having%20already%20produced%20a%20few%20fine%20cameos%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20there%20are%20many%20who%20wonder%20why%20the%20franchise%20isn't%20sending%20Thala%20up%20the%20order%2C%20at%20a%20position%20where%20his%20explosiveness%20can%20benefit%20the%20team%20more.%20After%20the%20defeat%20against%20the%20Royals%2C%20CSK%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Stephen%20Fleming%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F187-stephen-fleming-playerprofile%5C%22%3EStephen%20Fleming%3C%2Fa%3E%20solved%20this%20mystery%2C%20putting%20the%20topic%20to%20bed%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20burning%20topic%20of%20Dhoni's%20batting%20position%2C%20Fleming%20said%20that%20the%20former%20India%20captain's%20knees%20aren't%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20not%20feasible%20for%20him%20to%20bat%20for%2010-12%20overs%20in%20match%2C%20considering%20he%20also%20keeps%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20it's%20a%20time%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleming%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BMS%20judges%20it.%20His%20body%20is%2C%20his%20knees%20aren't%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20And%20he's%20moving%20okay%2C%20but%20there's%20still%20an%20attrition%20aspect%20to%20it.%20He%20can't%20bat%2010%20overs%20running%20full%20stick.%20So%20he%20will%20gauge%20on%20the%20day%20what%20he%20can%20give%20us.%20If%20the%20game's%20in%20the%20balance%20like%20today%2C%20he%20will%20go%20a%20little%20bit%20earlier%2C%20and%20he%20backs%20other%20players%20when%20other%20opportunities%20are%20up.%20So%20he's%20balancing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFleming%20said%20that%20the%20ideal%20time%20for%20Dhoni%20to%20bat%20is%2013t