back-zelenskyy-memes-for-vp%2Famp_articleshow%2F119772157.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20started%20a%20nonprofit%20to%20fight%20ALS%20after%20my%20husband's%20death.%20Here's%20how%20tech%20and%20AI%20can%20help%20us%20find%20a%20cure.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peter%20Cohen%20and%20Indu%20Navar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e9701c63d72727e198a91f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221752%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIndu%20Navar%20and%20her%20late%20husband%2C%20Peter%20Cohen.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Indu%20Navar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIndu%20Navar%20has%20spent%20her%20career%20in%20tech%2C%20building%20and%20investing%20in%20organizations%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20founded%20the%20Peter%20Cohen%20Foundation%20and%20EverythingALS%20after%20her%20husband%20died%20of%20ALS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECohen%20had%20a%20long%20tech%20career%2C%20too.%20He%20built%20Amazon%20Mechanical%20Turk%20and%20AWS%20at%20Amazon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20As-Told-To%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Indu%20Navar%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20Founder%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.everythingals.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEverythingALS%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20been%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20building%20technology%20that%20changed%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20degrees%20in%20electrical%20engineering%20and%20computer%20science.%20I%20started%20my%20career%20at%20NASA%20and%20was%20on%20the%20founding%20team%20of%20what%20is%20today's%20WebMD.%20Then%2C%20I%20started%20another%20company%20that%20I%20ran%20for%2014%20years.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20was%20investing%20and%20advising.%20I've%20always%20been%20fascinated%20with%20big%20data%20and%20building%20analytics%20on%20top%20of%20it.%20My%20husband%2C%20Peter%20Cohen%2C%20worked%20at%20Amazon%20for%20about%2018%20years.%20He%20joined%20around%201996%20or%201997%20and%20built%20Amazon%20Mechanical%20Turk%2C%20a%20crowd-sourcing%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20was%20really%20good.%20Here%20we%20are%20making%20change.%20He%20was%20still%20in%20his%20late%20forties%2C%20and%20then%20he%20started%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I%20think%20something%20is%20wrong%20with%20my%20ankle.%20It's%20not%20dorsal%20flexing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20no%20big%20deal%2C%20it's%20just%20an%20ankle%20issue.%26quot%3B%20No%2C%20it%20was%20a%20spine%20issue.%20Oh%20no%2C%20it%20was%20a%20brain%20issue.%20It%20took%20us%20two%20years%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20it%20was%20actually%20ALS%2C%20which%20is%20degenerative.%20The%20method%20of%20diagnosing%20ALS%20is%20called%20elimination%2C%20so%20you%20eliminate%20other%20diseases%20and%20problems.%20I%20think%20we%20spent%20over%20%24100%2C000%20just%20to%20diagnose%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%2090%20minutes%2C%20somebody%20is%20getting%20diagnosed%20with%20ALS%2C%20and%20they're%20hearing%20the%20same%20diagnosis%20they%20heard%2080%20years%20ago.%20You%20have%202%20to%205%20years%20to%20live%20from%20your%20first%20symptom.%20That's%20what%20shocked%20me.%20It%20takes%20a%20long%20time%20to%20get%20diagnosed%2C%20and%20we%20diagnose%20late%20compared%20to%20other%20diseases%2C%20like%20cancer.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20pass%20away%20without%20even%20being%20diagnosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20was%20diagnosed%20in%202018%20and%20passed%20away%20in%202019.%20It%20shook%20us.%20It%20shook%20us%20in%20a%20way%20that%2C%20as%20entrepreneurs%20and%20as%20problem%20solvers%2C%20we%20ask%20how%20this%20is%20in%20such%20a%20dire%20state%20where%20we%20haven't%20done%20something%20about%20it%20in%2080%20years%3F%20This%20problem%20is%20very%20opaque%20until%20you've%20gone%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20a%20nonprofit%20in%20his%20name%20called%20the%20Peter%20Cohen%20Foundation.%20My%20goal%20is%20to%20be%20able%20to%20say%20that%20he%20helped%20cure%20ALS%20with%20what%20he%20went%20through.%20We%20used%20to%20talk%20all%20the%20time%20about%20what%20we%20would%20do%20differently%20if%20we%20knew%20this%20problem%20existed%20before%20it%20happened%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20goal%20with%20the%20Peter%20Cohen%20Foundation%20and%20EverythingALS%20is%20to%20bring%20technology%20innovations%20to%20ALS%20and%20other%20neurodegenerative%20diseases.%20We%20do%20everything%20from%20monitoring%20and%20assessing%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20clinical%20trials%20and%20using%20sensors%20to%20predict%20what%20will%20happen.%20The%20sensors%20measure%20patients'%20speech%2C%20breathing%2C%20walking%2C%20and%20fine%20motor%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20don't%20actually%20have%20the%20tools%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20the%20drug%20you%20give%20a%20patient%20is%20really%20working%20because%20the%20way%20they%20evaluate%20your%20deterioration%20is%20by%20asking%20you%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20a%20scale%20of%201%20to%204%2C%20how%20is%20your%20speech%3F%20How%20is%20your%20walking%3F%20How%20easy%20is%20it%20for%20you%20to%20cut%20your%20food%3F%26quot%3B%20For%20us%2C%20we're%20vegetarians.%20We%20don't%20cut%20our%20food%2C%20so%20how%20would%20we%20know%20how%20to%20answer%20that%3F%20It's%20called%20a%20patient-reported%20outcome%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20questioning%20has%20not%20evolved%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20using%20sensors%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20you%20to%20get%20to%20the%20point%20where%20you%20can't%20do%20things.%20We%20can%20actually%20predict%20where%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20in%203%2C%206%2C%209%2C%20or%2012%20months.%20We'll%20use%20them%20for%20early%20diagnosis.%20We've%20digitized%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20our%20algorithm%20is%20in%20clinical%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20call%20it%20citizen-driven%20research%20because%20we%20go%20directly%20to%20patients%20and%20do%20research%20with%20people%20who%20are%20being%20affected%20by%20the%20disease%2C%20so%20we%20can%20get%20thousands%20of%20people%20involved.%20We%20send%20the%20sensors%20to%20them%2C%20they%20wear%20them%2C%20and%20we%20monitor%20them%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20EverythingALS%20app%20that%20lets%20patients%20talk%20to%20others%20who%20have%20ALS%20and%20have%20gone%20through%20this%20journey.%20They%20can%20also%20talk%20to%20our%20LLM-based%20generative%20AI%20tool%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20like%20talking%20to%20ChatGPT.%20Our%20AI%20is%20really%20walled%20off%20and%20trained%20only%20with%20the%20data%20we%20have%20and%20the%20220%20hours%20of%20experts%20who%20have%20spoken%20to%20us.%20It's%20a%20very%20trusted%20dataset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20we%20are%20moving%20to%20applying%20our%20process%20to%20our%20first%20other%20disease%2C%20which%20is%20Alzheimer's.%20Huntington's%20and%20Parkinson's%20will%20be%20in%20the%20near%20future%20as%20well.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20move%20the%20needle%20and%20fill%20the%20gap.%20We%20just%20felt%20like%20there%20was%20an%20unmet%20need%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20we%20care%20for%20people%2C%20and%20if%20you%20don't%20care%20for%20people%2C%20you'll%20never%20come%20up%20with%20a%20cure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findu-navar-nonprofit-everything-als-ai-tech-silicon-valley-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743364686000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e9741669253ccddf9ab748%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findu-navar-nonprofit-everything-als-ai-tech-silicon-valley-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20her%20husband%20passed%20away%20from%20ALS%2C%20Indu%20Navar%20started%20an%20organizat