%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%C2%A0Thackeray's%20comments%20came%20amid%20demands%20by%20right-wing%20outfits%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20Aurangzeb's%20tomb%20located%20in%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20district.%20Protests%20over%20the%20issue%20had%20also%20triggered%20violence%20in%20Nagpur%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20we%20want%20to%20let%20the%20world%20know%20that%20these%20people%20sought%20to%20destroy%20the%20Marathas%20but%20were%20wiped%20out%20instead.%20Stop%20reading%20history%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20rather%20delve%20into%20history%20books%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20people%20not%20to%20get%20provoked%20and%20distracted%2C%20he%20said%20that%20socio-political%20situations%20were%20different%20in%20pre-Shivaji%20and%20post-Shivaji%20eras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20forgotten%20the%20real%20issues%20of%20the%20present%20time.%20Hindus%20who%20feel%20awakened%20after%20a%20movie%20are%20of%20no%20use.%20Did%20you%20learn%20about%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj's%20sacrifice%20because%20of%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20and%20about%20Aurangazeb%20because%20of%20Akshaye%20Khanna%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20recently%20released%20period%20drama%20'Chhaava'%2C%20based%20on%20the%20life%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%2C%20who%20was%20tortured%20and%20executed%20by%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Aurangzeb%20was%20born%20in%20Dahod%2C%20Gujarat.%20Those%20who%20provoke%20people%20for%20their%20selfish%20political%20aspirations%20are%20not%20concerned%20with%20history%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%C2%A0Thackeray%20said%20a%20country%20cannot%20progress%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20and%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Turkey%20and%20how%20it%20%26quot%3Breformed%26quot%3B%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReligion%20should%20remain%20within%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20your%20home.%20A%20Hindu%20identifies%2