%20and%20water.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPollution%2C%20including%20ocean%20acidification%2C%20microplastics%2C%20and%20waste%20dumping%2C%20also%20affects%20turtle%20populations%20long-term.%20%E2%80%9CSea%20turtles%20are%20bearing%20the%20impact%20of%20what%20we%20have%20done%20to%20the%20oceans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20hatcheries%2C%20predators%20like%20barn%20owls%2C%20dogs%2C%20and%20ants%20pose%20risks%20to%20the%20hatchlings.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20horrendous%20season%20where%20ants%20were%20killing%20hatchlings%20inside%20the%20nests%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Akila.%20To%20counter%20this%2C%20volunteers%20use%20natural%20deterrents%20like%20neem%20oil%20and%20turmeric%20while%20ensuring%20the%20doses%20are%20safe.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hatchery%20structure%20must%20also%20be%20secured%20with%20jute%20fencing%20to%20prevent%20hatchlings%20from%20wandering%20into%20danger%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akila%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERound-the-clock%20monitoring%20is%20essential%2C%20yet%20finding%20committed%20volunteers%20remains%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CEnsuring%20people%20guarding%20the%20hatchery%20are%20actually%20watching%20the%20nests%20is%20a%20task%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akila.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ocean%20is%20filled%20with%20danger%20for%20the%20turtles%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20SSTCN%20has%20protected%20Olive%20Ridley%20turtles%20along%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20coast.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20prevented%20local%20extinction%2C%20ensuring%20turtles%20continue%20to%20return.%20%E2%80%9CThanks%20to%20these%20sustained%20efforts%20for%20the%20past%2050%20years%2C%20the%20turtles%20haven%E2%80%99t%20gone%20extinct%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20where%20the%20volunteer%20body%20must%20have%20released%20several%20lakh%20baby%20turtles%20into%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESSTCN%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20turned%20Che